{"article_id":"4vqOsvlsJghUs6e6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Florida has ordered a machine recount of votes for state governor and senator","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"following last week 's closely fought mid-term elections ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"officials say .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Florida Secretary of State Ken Detzner said","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"as unofficial results in both races had fallen within a margin of 0.5 % ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"a recount was required by law .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"The two ballots are among the most important","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"yet to be decided .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"US President Donald Trump responded to the news","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"by accusing Democrats of trying to `` steal '' the elections .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The state 's Republican Governor Rick Scott ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who is standing for the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"also warned of electoral fraud ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"but neither he nor President Trump offered any evidence","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to back their claims .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The recounts are expected to take several days ,","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"but analysts say","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"possible legal challenges mean it could take weeks for the winners to be confirmed .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Mr Detzner has ordered","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that all 67 Florida counties complete machine recounts for the Senate and gubernatorial races by 15:00 local time on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"If a machine recount shows a difference of 0.25 % or less between the candidates ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the state will proceed to a hand recount","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that must conclude by 18 November ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"local media report .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"In the race for Florida 's Senate seat , unofficial results revealed a gap of just 0.15 % between the votes for incumbent Democrat Bill Nelson and Mr Scott .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Democrat Andrew Gillum had already conceded the state governorship ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"but Ron DeSantis 's lead for the Republicans later narrowed to 0.41 % .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"After the recount was announced ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Mr Gillum said :","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"`` I am replacing my words of concession with an uncompromised and unapologetic call","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"that we count every single vote . ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Mr DeSantis , however , insisted","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that the results were `` clear and unambiguous ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"just as they were on election night '' .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"`` It is important that everyone","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"involved in the election process","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"strictly adhere to the rule of law","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"which is the foundation for our nation , ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Mr Trump had earlier said","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"there was `` a lot of dishonesty '' over contested votes .","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"Some candidates have already launched legal action .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Mr Scott ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"who claimed victory on Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"is suing officials over an election recount ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"while Mr Nelson is suing over uncounted ballots","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"- and there have also been a number of protests outside the elections office .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Mr Scott called on sheriffs in every county to closely monitor the recount process ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"tweeting :","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"`` We will not let unethical liberals steal this election !","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"`` It 's time","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Senator Nelson accepts these results","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"and allows the state of Florida to move forward to a better future . ''","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"In one of his three lawsuits against election overseers , Mr Scott has asked a judge to impound voting machines and ballots","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"when they are not in use .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Mr Nelson responded to the legal action in a statement on Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"his rival , the state 's outgoing governor , was making `` false and panicked '' voter fraud claims","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"because he was afraid of losing .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"`` If Rick Scott wanted to make sure","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"every legal ballot is counted ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he would not be suing","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to try and stop voters from having their legal ballot counted","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"as intended , ''","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"said the Democratic incumbent .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Authorities have meanwhile shot down a conspiracy theory about ballot fraud .","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"Florida Senator Marco Rubio was among those","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"who retweeted a photo","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"showing a box","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"labelled `` provisional ballots ''","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"found at a school ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"raising concerns about possible foul play .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"But election officials stated","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that the box contained only supplies .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Mr Trump told reporters on Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"before leaving for Paris","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"to commemorate the 100th anniversary of the end of World War One ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"that he believed","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"that Mr Scott had clearly won the election .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"The president said","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"he would send his lawyers to Florida","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"`` to expose the fraud '' ,","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"calling the Nelson campaign 's recount lawyer Marc Elias an election stealer .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Florida has a history with close elections .","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"In 2000 , George W Bush and Al Gore faced an impasse","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"with the presidential vote hanging in the balance amid weeks of legal wrangling .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Mr Gore 's fate was finally sealed by a US Supreme Court ruling","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that said","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"in essence","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that time had run out for recounts in the crucial state ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"granting Mr Bush the presidency .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"In Georgia 's gubernatorial election , Democrat Stacey Abrams is refusing to concede in her race against Republican Brian Kemp .","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"Mr Kemp declared victory on Wednesday with a narrow lead","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"but campaign officials for Ms Abrams have started a legal challenge","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"to ensure all votes are counted .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Her supporters have claimed","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"that issues such as ballot machines","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"supplied","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"without power cables","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"and four-hour queues unfairly helped Mr Kemp .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"An ongoing tally has whittled Mr Kemp 's lead slightly to under 60,000 votes ,","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"the Atlanta Journal-Constitution reports .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"But Ms Abrams still needs another 22,000 votes","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"to trigger a run-off election next month ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"and it is unclear how many ballots remain outstanding .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"In Arizona , another tight senate race has yet to conclude between two US congresswomen","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"- Republican Martha McSally and Democrat Kyrsten Sinema .","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"With mail-in votes still being counted ,","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"Ms Sinema had widened her narrow lead to more than 30,000 votes by Sunday","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"( 1.4| % ) ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"US media report .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":186,"right":222,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":151,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":130,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":127,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":120,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":114,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":113,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":117,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":3,"right":116,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":4,"right":115,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":121,"right":125,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":121,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":16,"right":128,"relation":"adversative","nuc